import React from 'react';
import {
  HeaderWrapper,
  HeaderContainer,
  CompanyName,
  ItemContainer,
  Item,
  MenuContainer,
  Login,
  CartWrapper,
} from './HeaderComponents'
import { FaCart } from 'react-icons/fa'

const Header = () => {
  return (
    <HeaderWrapper>
      <HeaderContainer>
        <CompanyName>WISELY</CompanyName>
        <ItemContainer>
          <Item to="#">제품보기</Item>
          <Item to="#">브랜드 스토리</Item>
          <Item to="#">블로그</Item>
          <Item to="#">고객센터</Item>
        </ItemContainer>
        <MenuContainer>
          <Login to="#"></Login>
          <CartWrapper>
            <FaAndroid />
          </CartWrapper>
        </MenuContainer>
      </HeaderContainer>
    </HeaderWrapper>
  );
}

export default Header;
